Nightmare IV SimulEfun: clower_case()

string clower_case(string str);

DESCRIPTION
works like lower_case but will ignore and leave color codes alone.

EXAMPLES
clower_case("%%^^BOLD%%^^EXAMPLE",); will return "%%^^BOLD%%^^example
clower_case("BOLD%%^^EXAMPLE",); will return bold%%^^example

LOCATION
/adm/simul_efun/strings.c

SEE ALSO 
lower_case(), upper_case, cupper_case
